title: Jussie Smollett Indictment, Kylie Jenner, Obama, Reality Update and more.
itunes:title: Jussie Smollett Indictment, Kylie Jenner, Obama, Reality Update and more.
description:
We open the show today with gaming nostalgia.  What are the appropriate questions to ask before entering into a long term relationship?  Jussie Smollett has been indicted for filing a false police report.  Kylie Jenner caught between BFF and sister.  Sheryl Underwood has an interesting theory regarding Jussie Smollett's case.  Miss Carla's Reality Update covers Real Housewives of Atlanta and more.  Obama and Steph Curry had an event in Oakland and they both talked about Steph's 3 point shot among other topics.  Closing Remarks today covers wanting more and asking for more.  Have a great weekend!
